name: Cycles
description: Cycles is an experimental book, made with analog generative art, scanning and other methods. It is given to the community of hicetnunc as it should not rot away on my harddrive. The copy/text is not from me and coming from various sources - this means this work is under the CC BY-NC-SA licence. Do not resell it! Everything else, from the layout to the images is from me. Best viewed in two-pages cover mode. @somaticbits
